         <abstract id="aspace_97c7909cb5a654419f9fbadf929e86d5">The papers consist of photocopies of letters written by Charles Morgan Coit to his mother, sister, and brother George during the Civil War. Also included are photocopies of letters written by George Coit to his mother and sister and a photocopy of a letter by Mary Coit.</abstract>
